*** Settings ***
Library           RequestsLibrary


*** Keywords ***

Get Calculation JSON
    [Arguments]    ${num1}    ${num2}
    ${resp}=     GET    http://127.0.0.1:8888/plus/${num1}/${num2}

    # Verify the status code is 200 (OK)
    Should Be Equal    ${resp.status_code}    ${200}

    # Get the response content as a JSON object
    [return]    ${resp.json()}


